# The web gallery reads skills straight from this repo's skills/ folder, so it
# needs no database or secrets. These two only matter if you fork the library
# into a different GitHub repo — they point the install command and the upload
# PR flow at your fork. Defaults to SamRome1/devrel-skills@main.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GITHUB_REPO=your-org/your-repo
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GITHUB_BRANCH=main
